  "synopsis": "A hundred years ago, Chu Xiu transmigrated to the Empyrean Continent and rose as a fearsome villain—only to be hunted down and destroyed. Reborn with his memories intact, he's done playing the glaringly obvious bad guy. This time, Chu Xiu will grow stronger in the shadows, posing as a righteous hero admired by all while secretly manipulating fate itself. With a gamelike system at his side and a new strategy in mind, he'll rewrite his doomed future. After all, the most dangerous villain is the one no one sees coming.\n\n(Source: Tappytoon)",
